Spokesman on Indonesian Situation
BEIJING , November 15 ( Xinhua ) -- Foreign Ministry Spokesman Tang Guoqiang said today that China is concerned with the present situation in Indonesia as clashes and bloodshed incidents occurred in Jakarta recently .
In response to a question , Tang said that as a close friendly neighbor of Indonesia , China sincerely hopes that Indonesia will be able to maintain political and social stability , and that its people of all ethnic groups live in peace and work in contentment .
